Dialogue: 0,0:00:-01.00,0:00:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inherited will...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.64,0:00:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The tide of the times...\NPeople's dreams...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.54,0:00:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These things cannot be stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.38,0:00:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as people\Nseek the answer of freedom,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.48,0:00:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,these things will never cease to be!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.03,0:00:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only believe in the future --\NI don't care if anyone laughs
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.20,0:00:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That racing passion makes you shine
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.54,0:00:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too bright,\Nbut I want to gaze at it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.54,0:00:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sense "aesthetics" somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.15,0:00:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really really stuck on you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.55,0:00:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I follow, follow in the footsteps\Nof a dream that resembles no one
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.99,0:00:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until I dramatically get it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.33,0:01:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe In Wonderland!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.14,0:01:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to catch, catch the shape\Nof a dream no one can see
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.44,0:01:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to go with you,\Nso passionate feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.58,0:01:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really\Nneed everything to add up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.59,0:01:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather than run-of-the-mill daily life,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.76,0:01:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,run for paradise instead
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.36,0:01:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe In Wonderland!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.07,0:01:37.65,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Yuba" "Erumalu" "Nanohana" "Katorea"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.67,0:01:41.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three years have passed since\Na single drop of rain fell
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.94,0:01:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in the kingdom of oases.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.34,0:01:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The burning land is now\Nenveloped by a sad bellowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.28,0:01:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As Luffy and company left\Nthe green city of Erumalu
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.72,0:01:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for the Yuba oasis,\Nwhere the rebel army is,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.62,0:02:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they met sand pirates, and set out\Nafter attaining new friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.89,0:02:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"False Fortitude!\NCamu, Rebel Soldier at Heart!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.64,0:02:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahead is a village called Ido.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.87,0:02:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should be able to get water there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.31,0:02:18.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You're not coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.51,0:02:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We sand pirates can't\Ngo any further ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.91,0:02:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This land belongs to the people
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.52,0:02:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who've lived and died here\Nfor generations, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.45,0:02:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that how it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.99,0:02:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. The desert is the land of the free.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.52,0:02:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But not everyone can\Nsurvive in the harsh desert.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.93,0:02:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The village ahead is a place\Nwhere such people eke out a living.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.53,0:02:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what're you gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.20,0:02:46.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing much!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.67,0:02:50.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've freely lived as we pleased\Non this ocean of sand,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.34,0:02:52.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and that's what we'll keep on doing!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.85,0:02:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just like us, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.55,0:03:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah? That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.15,0:03:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--So long!\N--Take care!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.82,0:03:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See ya, old umbrella guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.63,0:03:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--They were great guys!\N--Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.70,0:03:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, where'd your brother go?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.90,0:03:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dunno. But he's Ace.\NNothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.90,0:03:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll suddenly show up\Nagain out of nowhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.70,0:03:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you keep making\Nsuch groundless claims?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.57,0:03:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyways, let's hurry to this Udo village!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.81,0:03:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--You mean Ido.\N--Ido?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.65,0:03:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.85,0:03:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's a desert pirate flag!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.09,0:03:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap! I gotta tell Big Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.93,0:03:48.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you utterly are rebel army soldiers!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.50,0:03:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since you and your\Ncompanions arrived, Camu-sama,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.47,0:03:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,attacks on the village\Nhave utterly stopped!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.21,0:04:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup! You'd have to be\Npretty crazy to take us on!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.08,0:04:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rest easy and leave it to us, Mayor!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.15,0:04:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! You're utterly correct!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.99,0:04:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But word is the rebel army and the\Nroyal army will be clashing soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.79,0:04:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Won't staying in a place\Nlike this interfere with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.16,0:04:21.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, we can't just leave a\Nplace that lets us eat all we--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.67,0:04:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, this is this, that is that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.57,0:04:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We may be rebels, but we haven't\Ncompletely given up on the king!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.21,0:04:35.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, we have utter faith\Nin the king as well,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.78,0:04:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so we were hoping things\Ncould be handled carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.79,0:04:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say no more!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.76,0:04:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After careful consideration, we've\Ndecided to keep you guys safe, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.86,0:04:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All we ask for in return\Nis booze and food!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.53,0:04:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.10,0:04:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I must be going now...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.97,0:05:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Bro Camu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.31,0:05:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would giving up on the king\Nmake us real rebel soldiers?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.88,0:05:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, get real.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.84,0:05:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't leave this village until\Nwe've sucked all of its sweet nectar!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.69,0:05:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Bro! Terrible news, Big Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.52,0:05:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?!\NPipe down, I'm trying to eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.89,0:05:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sand pirates!\NSand pirates are attacking!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.37,0:05:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For real?! What do we do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.00,0:05:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?!\NThere's nothing we can do against them!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.11,0:05:37.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we can't stick our tails\Nbetween our legs and run, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.58,0:05:42.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell us, Big Bro! What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.51,0:05:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Let's stick our tails\Nbetween our legs and run!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.08,0:05:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're running away?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.85,0:05:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what happens after we run away?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.69,0:05:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Live on the edge of starvation again?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.89,0:05:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You moron! Staying alive is all that matters!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.89,0:05:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are plenty of other villages like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.96,0:06:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now let's scram!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.63,0:06:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's for sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.80,0:06:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.61,0:06:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You cowards got real guts to\Ncall yourselves rebel soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.01,0:06:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you ask me, it's a pretty despicable\Nthing for four grown men to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.18,0:06:19.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell're you?!\NMind your own business!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.45,0:06:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When did you get in here, anyway?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.42,0:06:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Food thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.89,0:06:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.16,0:06:33.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes, yes! I'm sorry, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.53,0:06:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This place has good food.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.10,0:06:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.04,0:06:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry! I now realize\Nyou're no ordinary person!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.48,0:06:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As you can see, we stand no\Nchance at all against sand pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.78,0:06:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please lend us your help!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.99,0:06:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm. I'm not against the idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.46,0:07:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but on one condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.29,0:07:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Anything you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.96,0:07:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.60,0:07:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hey!\N--Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.20,0:07:14.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's where he was?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.71,0:07:15.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.74,0:07:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! So you're the sand pirates?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.94,0:07:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What do you mean?\NWe just left the sand pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.35,0:07:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Really? Well, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.55,0:07:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyways, great news, Luffy!\NI brought plenty of food and water!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.32,0:07:34.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Much appreciated!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.89,0:07:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This should be more than\Nenough for a good while!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.43,0:07:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace is incredible...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.90,0:07:43.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's for sure! He's nothing like\Na certain little brother we know!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.57,0:07:44.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can say that again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.87,0:07:48.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I was so thirsty...\N--Oh! Drink up, drink up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.17,0:07:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.57,0:07:52.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, Ace-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.48,0:07:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I assume you don't have\Nthe money for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.11,0:07:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you stole\Nit from that village...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.32,0:08:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing of the sort!\NThe rebel army gave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.29,0:08:04.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The rebel army?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.06,0:08:07.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I should say "clearly fake\Nrebel soldiers" to be more precise.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.86,0:08:11.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Eh?\N--Fake? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.26,0:08:13.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Basically, they call\Nthemselves rebel soldiers
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.60,0:08:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and were hired to protect the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.23,0:08:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The villagers are so grateful that\Nthey've been completely fooled.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.30,0:08:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're really just some hoodlums.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.54,0:08:27.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And they're bodyguards?\NWouldn't they get found out right away?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.18,0:08:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, the mere\Nmention of the rebel army
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.22,0:08:32.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will send most bandits running.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.18,0:08:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's real convenient.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.89,0:08:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Makes money and prestige come\Nrolling your way on its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.06,0:08:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rebel soldiers aren't hoodlums,\Nnor does the title serve as decoration.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.27,0:08:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vivi-chan. Should we teach 'em a lesson?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.27,0:08:58.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I dunno. Duping the villagers isn't\Nso different from what bandits do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.54,0:09:02.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the very least, the villagers\Nlive in peace with them around.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.78,0:09:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Should we get 'em just the same?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.48,0:09:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, big brother. Consider it\Nfrom Vivi-chan's perspective.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.85,0:09:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Surely you'd want to\Npulverize people like them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.86,0:09:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, she should do what she wants.\NI only gave my own thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.53,0:09:21.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to hear your excuses!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.13,0:09:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I waited all alone in the\Nmiddle of this vast desert!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.17,0:09:30.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no reason to\Ncover for these bastards.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.61,0:09:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not. I just know you\Nguys are in a hurry here...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.71,0:09:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that the kingdom can't keep\Nwatch over every little place,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.79,0:09:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there's nothing wrong with\Nvillages upholding public safety
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.12,0:09:45.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,on their own whenever possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.29,0:09:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.06,0:09:50.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. I want to test them first.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.50,0:09:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Test?\N--Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.66,0:09:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If these impostor rebel soldiers\Ntruly wish to protect the villagers,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.50,0:10:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think it matters\Nwhat they call themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.17,0:10:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you want to test what's\Nin their hearts, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.68,0:10:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. So, I hate to ask, but there's\Nsomething I'd like you all to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.75,0:10:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No sweat, Vivi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.99,0:10:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Things are\Ngetting interesting now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.72,0:10:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? It's going to be interesting?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.46,0:10:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on, Luffy! This isn't\Ngoing to be a game! Understand?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.26,0:10:26.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.03,0:10:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're basically gonna beat these\Nfake rebel guys up, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.07,0:10:34.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't understand a thing!\NSomeone do something about him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.34,0:10:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's been gone a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.34,0:10:39.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been almost an hour since he said,\N"Leave it to me!" and left...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.85,0:10:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You saw his strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.85,0:10:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet he's beating the\Nsand pirates up as we speak!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.28,0:10:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, think about who he's fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.05,0:10:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They might've beaten him\Nbefore he even got a chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.95,0:10:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In which case, we're next, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.39,0:10:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I can't do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.56,0:10:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate to lose such good room and board...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.33,0:10:58.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but staying alive is all that matters!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.20,0:11:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.88,0:11:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Good luck!\N--We're counting on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.95,0:11:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--You can do it!\N--Camu-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.05,0:11:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Camu-sama! We're relying on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.69,0:11:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was utterly about\Nto come calling for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.03,0:11:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I should've known you already\Nknew the sea pirates were here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.93,0:11:35.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?! Sea pirates?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.60,0:11:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not sand pirates?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.10,0:11:39.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's correct. Sea pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.77,0:11:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're far more\Nferocious than sand pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.94,0:11:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus one is a special-edition pirate\Nwith a 30 million-Berry bounty!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.71,0:11:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once we heard you were going to go,\N"Hiyaaah!" and get rid of them,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.78,0:11:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we were so utterly moved and grateful!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.49,0:11:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We know you can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.16,0:12:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck, mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.66,0:12:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't lose to some stupid sea pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.99,0:12:07.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna get strong just like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.93,0:12:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.71,0:12:16.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, Big Bro. Are you serious about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.78,0:12:19.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be stupid. Of course he isn't serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.74,0:12:21.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.98,0:12:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once we've left town, we run in\Nthe opposite direction of the pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.92,0:12:30.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We run to our last gasp!\NWhat other way is there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.69,0:12:38.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.27,0:12:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.61,0:12:50.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're following us...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.48,0:12:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a bunch of jerks...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.19,0:13:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright. We got one shot at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.89,0:13:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once we're out, immediately figure\Nout which direction is pirate-free
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.66,0:13:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and then run for your lives! Got it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.23,0:13:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotcha, loud and clear!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.96,0:13:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here goes! One! Two! Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.68,0:13:29.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh, crap...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.51,0:13:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get 'em, get 'em, rebel army!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.85,0:13:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give that a rest, will ya?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.87,0:13:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?! You're a rebel soldier?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.44,0:13:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, nothing of the sort!\NWe're just travelers passing through!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.88,0:14:01.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say your prayers, sea pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.85,0:14:08.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These rebel soldiers are gonna\Nmake mincemeat out of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.35,0:14:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be quiet, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.32,0:14:15.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right! How utterly rude of me!\NGood luck, Camu-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.83,0:14:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He seems especially spineless to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.50,0:14:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't seem reliable at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.43,0:14:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.57,0:14:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.80,0:14:28.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It might be best for the village\Nif we take care of them now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.51,0:14:32.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A little more. Let's watch\Nthings just a little more...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.14,0:14:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Get 'em, rebel soldiers!\N--You can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.45,0:14:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.12,0:14:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really are rebel soldiers after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.39,0:14:42.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, it isn't, uhh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.82,0:14:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What now, Big Bro?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.26,0:14:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We lost our chance to escape...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.89,0:14:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.00,0:14:53.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Ace-sama?\N--Please help...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.33,0:14:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is your fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.27,0:14:58.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try to get through it on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.00,0:15:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't do that! We're fakes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.54,0:15:05.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're men, act like it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.58,0:15:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How long are you gonna keep\Nup this petty crap of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.05,0:15:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do we do, Big Bro?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.55,0:15:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What do you mean, what do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.89,0:15:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have no choice now but to lie\Nour way out of this, impostor-style!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.00,0:15:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impostor-style?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.30,0:15:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, you! Don't be shocked\Nby what I have to say!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.14,0:15:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not the only rebel soldiers here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.24,0:15:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the village there are...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.91,0:15:40.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...100 million more soldiers like us!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.41,0:15:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, geez. That's worse than a kid's lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.95,0:15:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're no one to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.18,0:15:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! 100 million?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.99,0:15:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on, you!\NThat's not even believable!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.26,0:15:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's obviously bluffing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.96,0:15:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! It's a lie?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.09,0:15:56.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Obviously!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.26,0:15:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Oh, it was a lie?\N--Oh, geez!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.70,0:16:02.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You! How dare you trick me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.60,0:16:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! They realized I was lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.67,0:16:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you really think\Nthat would fool them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.87,0:16:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum Pistol!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.85,0:16:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.19,0:16:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He has Devil Fruit powers!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.96,0:16:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One hit knocked him out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.62,0:16:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not even rebel soldiers stand a\Nchance against something like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.69,0:16:33.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy, you idiot! It's all\Nover if you knock him out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.16,0:16:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what would we do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.41,0:16:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Brother Camu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.15,0:16:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.65,0:16:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sea pirate is coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.65,0:16:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--You can do it!\N--Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.22,0:17:04.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.67,0:17:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.43,0:17:13.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was a kid, I looked up\Nto the warriors of Alabasta
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.51,0:17:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and wanted to be as strong\Nas them someday...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.68,0:17:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, even now I do...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.85,0:17:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday, I want to be as strong\Nas the warriors I saw as a child...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.68,0:17:28.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.09,0:17:36.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How long are you gonna keep up\Nthis petty crap of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.27,0:17:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.58,0:17:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, we're fake rebel soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.55,0:17:59.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if all we want is to be as\Nstrong as the heroes we saw as kids,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.65,0:18:01.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we're just a bunch of scoundrels now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.95,0:18:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, even if my dream never comes true,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.66,0:18:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't take those kids' dreams away!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.56,0:18:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I'm no match for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.86,0:18:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to fight so that someday\Nthose kids can beat you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.47,0:18:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If my only other choice is to remain\Na punk in those kids' memories,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.54,0:18:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then I'd rather die as a hero right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.22,0:18:39.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.69,0:18:43.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.76,0:18:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's your deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.43,0:18:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll fight, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.17,0:18:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your dream is my dream, Big Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.97,0:18:58.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've done all sorts of petty\Nthings since we were kids,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.51,0:19:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but you were always there\Nto protect the weak, Big Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.75,0:19:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hyaaaa!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.62,0:19:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'll always be there with you, Big Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.42,0:19:19.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be a hero with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.83,0:19:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.70,0:19:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's for sure!\NWhat do we have to lose?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.97,0:19:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can show you my spirit, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.94,0:19:34.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! There's no running\Naway now, anyways!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.11,0:19:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.05,0:19:39.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're looking different now...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.18,0:19:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though part of it seems because\Ntheir backs are to the wall...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.89,0:19:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.96,0:19:46.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't think they\Ncould change like that
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.29,0:19:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,unless they're holding\Nsomething dear in their hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.83,0:19:51.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then... they're okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.90,0:19:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Let's go. We'll entrust\Nthis place to them for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.57,0:20:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Retreat! Retreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.18,0:20:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sea pirates or not, bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.71,0:20:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Over my dead body will I let you\Ntake one step into this village!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.45,0:20:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, now that's more like it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.92,0:20:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I can go beat up\NCrocodile without worrying!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.19,0:20:22.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whew! What a relief!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.46,0:20:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut your trap and come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.43,0:20:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those bastards!\NThose are rebel soldiers for ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.37,0:20:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen such strong people before!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.40,0:20:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I suck at plays like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.74,0:20:36.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.14,0:20:44.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What just happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.78,0:20:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Utterly well done, rebel soldiers!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.81,0:21:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hey, Luffy!\N--Oh, Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.44,0:21:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How long are we gonna run?!\NThe act's over by now, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.55,0:21:20.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The way they abandoned\Ntheir lives was scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.59,0:21:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.72,0:21:30.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Protect her to the death, Sand-Sand Clan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.36,0:21:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye, Vivi! Grow up to be a great princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.11,0:21:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like the adventurers\NI dreamed of when I was a child
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.92,0:21:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I continue on to the ends of emotion
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.02,0:22:03.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I scoop up my hands,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.03,0:22:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the sand and time\Nthat spills from them
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.63,0:22:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,show me that this is\Nwhat I was born to do
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.64,0:22:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's continue swimming\Nat a near-tumbling speed
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.72,0:22:36.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until we wash up someday\Non a white sandy beach
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.50,0:22:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,no one knows about
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.11,0:22:58.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Vivi. How are we going\Nto stop the rebel army?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.75,0:23:01.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When we get to Yuba,\NI'll meet him-- Koza-- first.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.65,0:23:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Koza?\N--We just need to beat him up, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.99,0:23:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Please stop!\N--Pay attention more!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.56,0:23:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is this Koza guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.39,0:23:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Koza is my friend, and the\Nleader of the rebel army!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.06,0:23:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.40,0:23:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Rebel Warrior Koza!\NThe Dream Vowed to Vivi!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.90,0:23:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
